@startuml
skinparam dpi 180
skinparam backgroundColor #F7F8FA
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 18
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 15
skinparam ArrowColor #53657A
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam activityBorderColor #C9D3DE
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam activityFontColor #172033
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor #7A8EA3
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #EEF3F7
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #EEF6FF
skinparam noteBorderColor #7CB7FF

title HyperAgent — Reliable order lifecycle
caption Persistence and reconciliation turn an LLM proposal into an idempotent exchange action.

start
:LLM returns a typed proposal;
:Pydantic validates strict schema\nand rejects unknown fields;

if (Valid response?) then (yes)
  :Calculate neutral consequences\nloss at stop · margin · funding · slippage;
  :One final model review\nKEEP_AS_IS · ADJUST · CANCEL;
else (no)
  :Fail closed to HOLD;
  :Persist parse incident;
  stop
endif

if (Final action executable?) then (yes)
  :Run deterministic operational checks;
else (no)
  :Persist decision and rationale;
  stop
endif

if (Operationally coherent?) then (yes)
  :Build deterministic decision key + cloid;
else (no)
  :Block invalid side effect;
  :Persist guardrail verdict;
  stop
endif

:Write durable PENDING intent\nbefore any network call;

if (Intent already exists?) then (yes)
  :Reuse existing intent;
  :Reconcile exchange truth;
else (no)
  :Submit signed order once;
endif

if (Acknowledgement unambiguous?) then (yes)
  :Persist exchange order and actual fills;
else (no)
  :Mark acknowledgement UNKNOWN;
  :Query open orders, history and fills;
endif

:Place / reconcile reduce-only protections\nonly when selected by the final plan;
:Reconstruct position, fees, funding\nand realized net P&L from exchange data;
:Expose complete trace in dashboard;
stop

floating note left
  Kill-switch is checked at cycle entry
  and again immediately before execution.
end note

legend bottom
  |= Invariant |= Result |
  | Strict contracts | Invalid model output cannot reach execution |
  | Persist before submit | A retry cannot invent a second intent |
  | Stable cloid | Duplicate submissions are detectable |
  | Reconcile ambiguous state | Network uncertainty is not blind-retried |
  | Exchange truth | Fills, fees and P&L remain reconstructable |
endlegend
@enduml
